     <div xml:lang="lat" type="encomium">
   <head>Ad <hi>Andream Morum,</hi> Petraei fontis detectorem,
<gap reason="foreign">
         <desc>〈 in non-Latin alphabet 〉</desc>
      </gap>
   </head>
   <l>
      <hi>PEtraei</hi> laticis gratas languentibus undas</l>
   <l>Detegis, &amp; tanti quae sit origo boni.</l>
   <l>Si tanta utilitas insit vulgaribus undis,</l>
   <l>Hasce sibi ut vulgus commoda prima putet;</l>
   <l>Quanta o Petraeo debetur gloria fonti;</l>
   <l>Omnigenis obstat quae Panacèa malis!</l>
   <l>Nymphae monstratis meruerunt Orgia lymphis:</l>
   <l>Quanta erit inventi gloria; <hi>More;</hi> tui?</l>
   <closer>
      <signed>T. CRAFORDIUS.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
